# Data Placeholder

Place your audio dataset here with the following structure:

```
data/raw/
├── genre1/
│   ├── audio1.wav
│   ├── audio2.wav
│   └── ...
├── genre2/
│   ├── audio1.wav
│   └── ...
└── ...
```

Supported audio formats: WAV, MP3, AU

Recommended datasets:
- GTZAN Genre Collection
- FMA (Free Music Archive) small
- Custom dataset with similar structure
